### Summary:  
- **Clinical Trial Update**: Translational data shows CHM CDH17 CAR-T cells persist for up to **six months** post-infusion in two subjects at **Dose Level 1** (out of 4).  
- **Target Validation**: CDH17 (cadherin 17) confirmed on tumour cells in all subjects.  
- **Trial Progress**: **Dose Level 2** enrollment ongoing; Phase 1/2 trial (NCT06055439) aims to enroll up to **15 patients** for dose selection.  

**No material trading or capital markets information identified.**
